         from local e-mags around the world,who are exchanging articles
         there, taking away new articles to use in their local  e-mags,
         and placing articles for each other mags.
           How  it  works?  Easy!  For now  we  have  a mailing list to
         discuss  everything,  and to  exchange  articles. Once someone
         from  your  country writes an  interesting  article you put it
         here  and all the world will  read this article after it! That
         sounds great, doesn't it? You put the articles from your e-mag
         to  our network, and we give you articles from our network for
