ø4 BBS's

 Morbid Incite was ran by Spoonman for about 4 or 5 years. MZ ran Room 101, JuD
 ran  "Don't  Panic", and Squidgalator ][ ran  The Deep Umbra. Several BBS's in
 the other states were run by people like Legend, Black Artist and Ozone.

ø4 Other scene institutions

 The Australian scene has a mailinglist and a web-page of its own. The name of
 the  mailinglist is scene-l, but the subscribers usually call it spam-l due to
 the  high  number of unserious mails. The  web-page  with the name scene.au is
 located at http://scene.ign.com.au/.








